1
00:00:01,466 --> 00:00:06,099
I understand that
you've been through a lot.

2
00:00:07,599 --> 00:00:08,599
Just don't forget.

3
00:00:10,099 --> 00:00:14,199
Everybody must face the consequences
of their actions.

4
00:00:16,833 --> 00:00:20,433
Does karma breathing?
Can it talk?

5
00:00:22,633 --> 00:00:26,233
I haven't seen karma
deal with bad people at all.

6
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,233
There's a plenty of bad people that
are successful.

7
00:00:29,733 --> 00:00:31,133
This world is messed up.

8
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:39,240
It's a good thing
that you didn't kill anyone.

9
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:46,266
I just worried and wish you well.

10
00:00:47,733 --> 00:00:54,666
These days, you do magic and charming spell,
I never go against you.

11
00:00:56,466 --> 00:00:59,666
It's what you like to do.

12
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:05,866
If you use those knowledge
for a good purpose,

13
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:08,000
it would be better.

14
00:01:09,533 --> 00:01:10,833
Please stop.

15
00:01:11,666 --> 00:01:12,966
I understand you.

16
00:01:18,533 --> 00:01:20,800
Thanks for supporting me all along.

17
00:01:22,699 --> 00:01:25,933
If you didn't help me out that day.

18
00:01:27,566 --> 00:01:29,400
I wouldn't survive.
